# Audio policy:
# .mp3 files in audio/ are committed only when small.
# Files larger than 5 MB should be stored elsewhere
# (for example an unlisted Vimeo upload or a dedicated audio bucket)
# and linked from the lesson tables rather than committed to the repo.
